sequenceDiagram
  autonumber
  participant P as Publisher
  participant S as messagingService
  participant PR as Provider (transport)
  participant H as Subscriber handler
  participant EV as EventPublisher port

  P->>S: publish({ topic, payload, ttlMs, retryPolicy })
  S->>S: build message (correlationId, expiresAt)
  S->>EV: MessagePublished
  alt message expired (TTL)
    S->>EV: MessageExpired
    S-->>P: { delivered: 0, expired: true }
  else deliver
    S->>PR: select(topic)  (one per group / pub-sub across groups)
    PR-->>S: [ targets ]
    loop each target
      S->>H: handler(message)
      alt ack (resolves)
        S->>EV: MessageDelivered
      else nack (throws) and retries remain
        S->>EV: MessageRetried
        S->>H: handler(message)  (retry, after delayMs)
      else retries exhausted
        S->>S: push to dead-letter
        S->>EV: DeadLettered
      end
    end
    S-->>P: { delivered, failed }
  end

  Note over P,S: request/reply
  P->>S: request({ topic }) → pending(correlationId)
  S->>H: handler(message with replyExpected)
  H->>S: reply(message, payload)
  S-->>P: resolve(payload)  (or RequestTimeoutError)
